<hymn_number>72</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Isaorana anie Jehovah,
 Andriamanitry ny Israely,
 Hatramin'ny taloha indrindra,
 Ka mandrakizay.

[V2]
 Ary aoka ny olona rehetra,
 Hanao hoe : &quot;Amena&quot; (Haleloia), &quot;Amena&quot;.</lyrics>
<title>ISAORANA ANIE JEHOVAH ASAFA72</title>
</song>